description:
&lt;p&gt;The Surgical Directorate at Taunton and Somerset NHS Foundation Trust are offering an exciting opportunity to support the Directorate Triumvirate in the delivery of the Covid-19 restoration and recovery plans for elective and emergency surgery.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Working to the Directorate Service Director (SD)and Associate Directorate Manager (ADM)the post holder will ensure the details, timescales and resources of the recovery plan are in place including a robust governance arrangement. The post holder will support Service Managers to deliver specialty restoration and recovery plans, including performance, financial accountability, human and physical resources, highlighting risks as appropriate.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you feel that you have the relevant qualifications, skills and experience, can make a difference to our patients and our successful service and would like further information or to visit, please do not hesitate to contact us.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameNicola FianderJob titleAssociate Directorate ManagerEmail addressnicola.fiander@somersetft.nhs.ukTelephone number01823 343936&lt;/p&gt;
